<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Alternative_solution_mim  Rule: alternative_solution_requires_solution_definition 
   <express_ref linkend="alternative_solution:mim:Alternative_solution_mim.alternative_solution_requires_solution_definition"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.alternative_solution_requires_solution_definition">
The <b>alternative_solution_requires_solution_definition</b> rule constrains every instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> that is a version of a <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product"/> of category 'alternative solution', to have exactly one definition of type 'alternative definition'.
<note>This rule corresponds to the restriction for alternative solutions of the rule <express_extref linkend="complex_product_requires_product_definition" standard="ISO 10303-214"/>.</note>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.alternative_solution_requires_solution_definition.wr:WR1">
There shall not be any <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation"/> of a <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product"/> of category 'alternative solution', that is not referred to by exactly one <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> whose name of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> is 'alternative definition'. </ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Alternative_solution_mim  Rule: restrict_alternative_definition 
   <express_ref linkend="alternative_solution:mim:Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_alternative_definition"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_alternative_definition">
The <b>restrict_alternative_definition</b> rule specifies the restrictions that apply to instances of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> that reference as <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> a <express_ref linkend="application_context_schema:ir_express:application_context_schema.product_definition_context"/> with name 'alternative definition'. 
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_alternative_definition.wr:WR1">
Any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> that references as its <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> a <express_ref linkend="application_context_schema:ir_express:application_context_schema.product_definition_context"/> with name 'alternative definition', shall be referred to as <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> by exactly one instance of 
<express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> with name 'alternative solution'.
<note>This instance relates the <express_ref linkend="alternative_solution:arm:Alternative_solution_arm.Alternative_solution"/> with the <express_ref
    linkend="alternative_solution:arm:Alternative_solution_arm.Alternative_solution.base_element"/> it specifies an alternate implementation for.</note>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_alternative_definition.wr:WR2">
Any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> that references as its <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> a <express_ref linkend="application_context_schema:ir_express:application_context_schema.product_definition_context"/> with name 'alternative definition', shall have its name attribute equal to 'technical', 'supplier', 'technical supplier', or ''.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_alternative_definition.wr:WR3">
Any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> that references as its <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> a <express_ref linkend="application_context_schema:ir_express:application_context_schema.product_definition_context"/> with name 'alternative definition' and that has a name attribute equal to 'supplier', 'technical supplier', shall be in the set of items of exactly one <express_ref
    linkend="person_organization_assignment:mim:Person_organization_assignment_mim.applied_organization_assignment"/> that has a role name 'supplier'. 
</ext_description>

<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Alternative_solution_mim  Rule: restrict_solution_category 
   <express_ref linkend="alternative_solution:mim:Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_solution_category"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.solution_definition_requires_solution_category">
The <b>solution_definition_requires_solution_category</b> rule constrains every instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> of type 'alternative definition' to be a definition of a <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product"/> of category 'alternative solution'.
<note>This rule corresponds to the restriction for alternative solutions of the rule <express_ref linkend="catalog_data_information:mim:Catalog_data_information_mim.restrict_product_definition_context_for_product"/>.</note>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.solution_definition_requires_solution_category.wr:WR1">
There shall not be any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/>, whose name of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> is 'alternative definition', that is not a definition of a <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product"/> of category 'alternative solution'.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_product_definitions_for_base_element">
The <b>restrict_product_definitions_for_base_element</b> rule restricts the name of instances of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> when they are related by a <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> with name 'solution alternative definition'.
The name of the relating <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> shall be 'alternative definition', 'functional definition' or 'conceptual definition'.
The name of the related <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> shall be 'alternative definition'.
<note>This rule corresponds to the constraint on the type of the attribute <express_ref linkend="alternative_solution:arm:Alternative_solution_arm.Alternative_solution.base_element"/>.</note>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Alternative_solution_mim.restrict_product_definitions_for_base_element.wr:WR1">
There shall not be any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> with name 'solution alternative definition', for which the name of the related instances of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> does not match the constraint mentioned above.
</ext_description>

